document_data.mainbody:
Tat Jansen was a child of the numerous gnome Jansen family in the late 14 century DR.
Just like her brother, Tot, Tat had fair skin and light brown hair.
In the , Tat and Tot lived in Athkatlas River District slums in the Jansens family home, along with Ma Jansen, Kylie Jansen, Jan Jansen, and Uncle Gerhardt. Tat was fiercely protective of her pet cat, yelling at guests who dared to lay their eyes on the beast.
